add INPUTFILE OUTPUTFILE IMGDIR ORIDIR CALIBFILE NAME : add a channel to a cloud
    INPUTFILE : path to the input ply cloud
    OUTPUTFILE : path to the output ply cloud
    IMGDIR : path to the directory containing the images
    ORIDIR : path to the MicMac generated orientation directory
    CALIBFILE : path to the xml calbiration file of the camera
    NAME : name of the channel to add to the cloud